Glass beach



This beach is on the site of the old Ft. Bragg dump. I could have spent hours here collecting driftglass.
Taken Thursday, July 05, 2001, 03:02:12pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 1015kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/320s @ F5.6, ISO 100, 47mm
PS6 Equalize, USM 20:20 - 100:0.5
